762
00:37:48,583 --> 00:37:49,792
A theory?

763
00:37:49,834 --> 00:37:52,375
I think Dr. Reyga's
shield does work.

764
00:37:53,875 --> 00:37:56,000
Return to the ship
immediately.

765
00:37:56,041 --> 00:37:57,959
I'm sorry.

766
00:37:59,625 --> 00:38:01,417
Mr. Worf, override
the shuttle's computer.

767
00:38:01,458 --> 00:38:02,709
Return it
