773
00:38:14,709 --> 00:38:16,333
She is too close
to the star.

774
00:38:16,375 --> 00:38:18,041
Solar interference
is too high.

775
00:38:18,083 --> 00:38:19,291
Mr. Data,
what is her heading?

776
00:38:19,333 --> 00:38:21,834
Bearing 271 mark 4, sir.

777
00:38:21,875 --> 00:38:24,542
She is headed
