787
00:38:50,333 --> 00:38:52,792
I'm not wrong.

788
00:38:52,834 --> 00:38:57,291
COMPUTER:
External temperature
1.9 million Kelvins.

789
00:39:03,083 --> 00:39:05,792
Sir, the shuttle
is entering the corona.

790
00:39:07,417 --> 00:39:09,083
Beverly,
