792
00:39:11,333 --> 00:39:14,834
Computer, shield status.

793
00:39:14,875 --> 00:39:16,709
COMPUTER:
Metaphasic shield holding.

794
00:39:16,750 --> 00:39:20,542
All systems within normal
operating parameters.

795
00:39:20,583 --> 00:39:23,417
Congratulations,
Dr. Reyga.

796
00:39:23,458 --> 00:39:25,333
You did it.

797
00:39:25,375 --> 00:39:27,709
Captain, I want you
to post security guards

798
00:39:27,750 --> 00:39:29,709
