800
00:39:31,500 --> 00:39:33,250
for sabotaging
the first test.

801
00:39:33,291 --> 00:39:34,208
I think if we...

802
00:39:34,250 --> 00:39:36,000
(<i> console beeping</i> )

803
00:39:37,834 --> 00:39:40,375
Sir, we have lost contact.

804
00:39:47,417 --> 00:39:49,625
Crusher to<i> Enterprise.</i>

805
00:39:49,667 --> 00:39:51,166
I've lost you.
Come in.

806
00:39:51,208 --> 00:39:55,250
CRUSHER:
<i>Justman</i> to<i> Enterprise.</i> 
Come in.

807
00:39:55,291 --> 00:39:58,500
<i>Enterprise,</i> do you hear me?
Come in.

808
00:39:58,542 --> 00:40:01,041
They cannot hear you.

809
00:40:01,083 --> 00:40:04,041
I have severed
communications.

810
00:40:04,083 --> 00:40:05,375
How can you be alive?

811
00:40:05,417 --> 00:40:07,917
I'd think
after your autopsy on me

812
00:40:07,959 --> 00:40:09,500
