the answer to that.

813
00:40:09,542 --> 00:40:12,041
The slow rate
of cellular decay.

814
00:40:12,083 --> 00:40:15,750
It is a natural result
of physiostasis.

815
00:40:15,792 --> 00:40:18,083
Takarans can control
their physiology

816
00:40:18,125 --> 00:40:19,667
at a cellular level.

817
00:40:19,709 --> 00:40:22,208
We can create
the appearance of death.

818
00:40:22,250 --> 00:40:25,500
In the morgue, you were
conscious the whole time.

819
00:40:25,542 --> 00:40:26,959
You heard everything
we said.

820
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,875
You knew everything
we were going to do.

821
00:40:28,917 --> 00:40:30,417
Move away.

822
00:40:31,583 --> 00:40:33,208
Move away.

823
00:40:40,625 --> 00:40:42,083
What are you doing?

824
00:40:42,125 --> 00:40:45,417
I'm sending out
a transient subspace signal.

825
00:40:45,458 --> 00:40:49,125
It will obscure the shuttle
from the<i> Enterprise</i> sensors

826
00:40:49,166 --> 00:40:52,792
