as a warp engine breach.

827
00:40:52,834 --> 00:40:55,417
They will believe that
you have been destroyed.

828
00:40:55,458 --> 00:40:57,750
I'd like
to thank you, doctor.

829
00:40:57,792 --> 00:40:59,083
For what?

830
00:40:59,125 --> 00:41:01,750
All I wanted to do
was discredit Reyga

831
00:41:01,792 --> 00:41:05,917
so that no one would pursue
his technology except me,

832
00:41:05,959 --> 00:41:10,458
