into a weapon.

835
00:41:17,917 --> 00:41:20,458
All I have to do
is wait here

836
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:22,667
until the<i> Enterprise</i> 
is convinced

837
00:41:22,709 --> 00:41:25,417
you are dead
